product.longDescription: The juiciness and crunch of an iceberg, with romaine sweetness, head shape, and hearts. Petite frame for easy pairing with other minis. Leaves have a beautiful "spoon" shape for small leaf wraps and hors d'oeuvres. Very high count of crunchy leaves that withstand handling very well. Forms nice hearts at full maturity. Extremely slow bolting. High resistance to downy mildew races EU 16–20, 22–25, 29, 30, 33–37 and Nasonovia ribisnigri aphid. MT0-30. Avg. 13,000 seeds/lb. Packet: 250 seeds.
product.shortDescription: Crunchy, snackable, stackable mini cosberg. Conventional seed with NOP-compliant pelleting.
